Sarah Prime is the Director of Product Technology, managing all things related to product, project, and people for the OWL Vision Platform. Sarah is no stranger to wearing many hats, spending the last 12 years creating roadmaps and project plans, writing requirements, and dreaming up new features for software applications, digital media, and educational publishing. She began her career at Cengage Learning, developing multimedia products and learning simulations grossing over $20M in annual revenue. Sarah graduated from Principia College with a BA in Mass Communication and is a Certified Scrum Master through Scrum Alliance. Sarah recently bought a house just north of Denver, CO.When she grows weary of home repairs, weeding, or landscaping, Sarah escapes to the mountains of Colorado for long hikes or snowshoe treks.























