Company Overview of OWL Cybersecurity, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
OWL Cybersecurity, LLC offers a dark net threat intelligence platform that allows organizations to understand and mitigate their digital exposure and risks. Its platform provides a range of assessment and consulting services, including risk analysis and threat intelligence, security consulting, penetration testing, application code review, incident response, and digital forensics. The company also develops solutions in maturity modeling; gap analysis; strategic road mapping; analysis and implementation of policies, procedures, and controls; compliance support and preparation; and executive security, threat, and protection analysis. OWL Cybersecurity, LLC was formerly known as One World Labs,...
OWL Cybersecurity, LLC offers a dark net threat intelligence platform that allows organizations to understand and mitigate their digital exposure and risks. Its platform provides a range of assessment and consulting services, including risk analysis and threat intelligence, security consulting, penetration testing, application code review, incident response, and digital forensics. The company also develops solutions in maturity modeling; gap analysis; strategic road mapping; analysis and implementation of policies, procedures, and controls; compliance support and preparation; and executive security, threat, and protection analysis. OWL Cybersecurity, LLC was formerly known as One World Labs, LLC and changed its name to OWL Cybersecurity, LLC in December 2015. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in Denver, Colorado.
Detailed Description


